text: Ic þurh muþ sprece mongum reordum, wrencum singe, wrixle geneahhe heafodwoþe, hlude cirme, healde mine wisan, hleoþre ne miþe, eald æfensceop, eorlum bringe blisse in burgum, þonne ic bugendre stefne styrme; stille on wicum <sittað> nigende.
Saga hwæt ic hatte, <þe> swa scirenige sceawendwisan hlude onhyrge, hæleþum bodige wilcumena fela woþe minre.
